OL,3,CFour teens arrested over wildfire
OL,4,C'started by a lighter'
OL,6,FPolice say a wildfire which caused
OL,7,F#30,000 of damage to farmers' crops
OL,8,Fwas sparked by a cigarette lighter.
OL,10,FThe blaze started in a barley field in
OL,11,FWoodthorpe, near York, on Sunday 12
OL,12,FJuly before sweeping across swathes of
OL,13,Ffarmland off Askham Lane, close to a
OL,14,Fhousing estate.
OL,16,FNorth Yorkshire Police said two girls
OL,17,Fpreviously arrested on suspicion of
OL,18,Farson are no longer being treated as
OL,19,Fsuspects, but remain under
OL,20,Finvestigation following a separate
OL,21,Ffire the same day.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
