CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1784395091
OL,3,CFour teens arrested over wildfire
OL,4,C'started by a lighter'
OL,6,FTwo other girls and two boys, all aged
OL,7,F14, have now been arrested.
OL,9,FA North Yorkshire Police spokesperson
OL,10,Fsaid: "An investigation indicated that
OL,11,Fthe fire was started using a lighter
OL,12,Fbefore rapidly spreading across the
OL,13,Ffield and becoming uncontrollable
OL,14,Fwithin a very short period of time."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
