CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1784395091
OL,3,CFour teens arrested over wildfire
OL,4,C'started by a lighter'
OL,6,FSgt Ben Ambler added: "This incident
OL,7,Fserves as a stark reminder of the
OL,8,Fdangers associated with fire-setting.
OL,9,FWhat may begin as a seemingly minor
OL,10,Fact can quickly escalate, causing
OL,11,Fextensive damage, placing lives at
OL,12,Frisk, and placing significant demands
OL,13,Fon emergency services.
OL,15,F"With the current warm, dry weather
OL,16,Fconditions, even a small flame can
OL,17,Fhave devastating consequences."
