PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1784395091
OL,3,CFour teens arrested over wildfire
OL,4,C'started by a lighter'
OL,6,FHe paid tribute to teenage farmers Jay
OL,7,FLoft and Cameron Bartram, who used
OL,8,Ftractors to create a firebreak to stop
OL,9,Fthe flames spreading to nearby houses.
OL,11,F"Their actions undoubtedly assisted in
OL,12,Flimiting the damage caused, and it is
OL,13,Fpleasing to see them receiving the
OL,14,Frecognition they deserve for their
OL,15,Fefforts," he said.
